org.smtlib.solvers

Class Solver_test

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.smtlib.solvers.Solver_test
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISolver
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Solver_cvc, Solver_simplify, Solver_yices

    public class Solver_test
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISolver
    This class is a Solver implementation that simply type-checks formulae and checks that commands are used correctly; it does not do any proving.

        exec - the executable for the solver, ignored for the case of this test solver
